    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Diis Manibus <lb n="2"/>Claudiae Prote <lb n="3"/>tu qui praeteriens spectas <lb n="4"/>monimentum meum aspice <lb n="5"/>quam indigne sit data vita <lb n="6"/>mea annorum septem vixi <lb n="7"/>dulcissima patri octavo <lb n="8"/>ingredie<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> animam deposui <lb n="9"/>meam noli doleri <note>sic</note> mater aetati <lb n="10"/>meae fatus quod voluit abstulit <lb n="11"/>te lapis obtestor leviter super <lb n="12"/>ossa quiescas ne tenerae aetati <lb n="13"/>tu gravis esse velis
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Marmor, weiß.</p>
            </div>
